🟢 PHASE 0 – PROJECT & BASE SETUP
🎯 Goal

Create a clean backend and admin web panel foundation.

🧠 Antigravity Prompt
Create a full-stack project structure for an Admin-only Cake Order Management System.

Backend:
- Node.js + Express
- Environment variable support
- JWT authentication
- Cloud SQL database (MySQL / PostgreSQL)
- ORM: Prisma
- REST API architecture

Admin Web:
- React.js
- Ant Design UI
- Routing setup
- Authentication context
- Protected routes

Backend base modules:
- auth
- users
- dashboard
- products
- variants
- orders
- payments
- customers
- notifications
- cashbook
- schedule

Ensure backend APIs are reusable and secure.

🟢 PHASE 1 – ADMIN AUTHENTICATION & ACCESS CONTROL
🎯 Goal

Secure admin access.

🧠 Antigravity Prompt
Implement admin authentication and authorization.

Backend:
- Admin user table
- Password hashing (bcrypt)
- JWT token generation
- Admin-only middleware
- Account status (ACTIVE / INACTIVE)

Admin Web:
- Login page
- Token-based authentication
- Protect all admin routes
- Logout functionality

